{"tid":1502192,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請用返Facebook，守著每一個輿論戰陣地","createTime":"2019-08-24T15:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T12:30:31.000Z","uid":19002,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c4793e3bf24abb1eead286b1f21278543c7020aa","tid":1502192,"uid":19002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:12:47.000Z","msg":"我明白依家好多人凈係用Instagram<br />\n每日係Instagram到Post好多反送中既野<br />\n但咁樣做其實意義唔係好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. Follow你既人好多時候都係同你同聲同氣。你不停Post，最多都係幫佢地update下新聞，但其實佢地有留意新聞notice可能已經見到<br />\n2. 你Post野既目的係咩?想多D人支持你?凈如我頭先所講，你既Followers好大部分本身已經支持，唔需要咁勤力係咁post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點解要post係Facebook?<br />\n1. 根本藍絲廢老只會用Facebook，所以你只可以係依度接觸並嘗試拉攏佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 藍絲同5毛好鍾意係Facebook到玩輿論，所以我地要係上面守著輿論，用事實同logic去打倒佢地同Fake News。當周邊環境一面倒支持反送中，佢地就會開始問自己係未企錯邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 其實中央係要俾錢去買email登記或者直接買AC，你係上面每Report一個5毛，佢就洗更多錢。同埋如果我地report到一班出名既，對佢地打擊係十分之大，對我地既士氣亦都有所提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，我希望大家唔好凈係用instagram，開始用返Facebook <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁當然，IG都唔可以放棄，隔離有個post講得好好，如果我地可以令外國名人係Instagram公開支持我地，其實對國際輿論有非常之大既影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5fc275b23d68e54249030790fc0b2ba7294eb0","tid":1502192,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:12:58.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e779ec64dafd05ed9a477a9c5b9c7641e8158a32","tid":1502192,"uid":19002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0371751ed191794ec29952e7e94ce037a1baadb7","tid":1502192,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"TWITTER"},{"pid":"9be91308edfe0c2f57e6348f675c2a014414f79e","tid":1502192,"uid":68802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:24:55.000Z","msg":"facebook有垃圾支持管理層del鳩你post ban鳩你account呀<br />\nnow可以del鳩你重點9分鍾呀<br />\n依兩日唔係侵侵order都唔會del鳩d五毛呀<br />\n打鳩完言論陣地戰就del account啦"},{"pid":"ec2f719a1b2b82dc439ac1aa6c73ef88cffa9434","tid":1502192,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:27:12.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n但最大威力一定係twitter"},{"pid":"5952f9cbcf6187218b67f4da1b4b1cee8cc98868","tid":1502192,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"FACEBOOK只係對廢老 同對內<br />\n真正最重要既戰場係TWITTER"},{"pid":"154979310061a4f952db50b05c1f2d79cc93fe73","tid":1502192,"uid":266372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:29:44.000Z","msg":"facebook Twitter 一定要大力推"},{"pid":"d675ffc64e4eaf362344c994035a240c034ffdd1","tid":1502192,"uid":266372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:30:05.000Z","msg":"Twitter 唔夠人手呀！！！！"},{"pid":"9d3f20921eaf125566405f2cc3bac6d198b02ead","tid":1502192,"uid":19002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d675ffc64e4eaf362344c994035a240c034ffdd1","tid":1502192,"uid":266372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:30:05.000Z","msg":"Twitter 唔夠人手呀！！！！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:34:50.000Z","msg":"Twitter真係好少人<br />\n每個post最多得100幾人<br />\n總之一個media都不能少"},{"pid":"f4d87ae7a8bc077ce5ec8ab3b7b98bc9200f6c78","tid":1502192,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d3f20921eaf125566405f2cc3bac6d198b02ead","tid":1502192,"uid":19002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d675ffc64e4eaf362344c994035a240c034ffdd1","tid":1502192,"uid":266372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-